 RJR Is Selling
@  Candy Brands
@  For $370 Million
@  ----
@  By Peter Waldman
@  Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal 
 <TIMEX3 functionInDocument="CREATION_TIME" temporalFunction="false" tid="t78" type="DATE" value="1989-10-30">10/30/89</TIMEX3> 
 WALL STREET JOURNAL (J) 
 RJR Z.NES 
